text: 80-years-young Essie Mayne was excited to be among the first to get the #COVID19 #vaccine yesterday at #myKHSC. She provides essential care for her husband Frank at Extendicare in #ygk. To all the long-term care staff getting vaccinated today, Essie says ‘there’s nothing to it.’ https://t.co/PaKhEi3YFi
